        "jsCode": "const tx=$('R Transactions').all().map(i=>i.json);\nconst transactions=tx.filter(r=>r && (r.timestamp||r.amount)).map(r=>({\n  date:(r.timestamp||'').trim(), amount:parseFloat(r.amount)||0, merchant:(r.merchant_vendor||'Unknown').trim(),\n  category:(r.category||'Other').trim(), need_or_want:(r.need_or_want||'Want').trim(), month_key:(r.month_key||'').trim()\n}));\nreturn [{json:{ monthly_income:140700, transactions, generated_at:new Date().toISOString() }}];\n"
